Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼 有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該是我的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計還有點痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過幸好傷勢沒大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍方來正式委託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 總之今天先好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天出來的診斷結果不錯的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.75,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}「我會更加努力」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.75,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}わたしはもっと がんばれるって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.82,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}曾向你如此許諾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.82,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}約束した きみと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:22.98,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}雖然討厭隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:22.98,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}隠しごとは キライだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:26.66,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}但不會給你看到我的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:26.66,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}痛みはみせないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:30.74,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}為了堅強地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:30.74,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}強く生きるために
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:34.43,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}上天賜予的這副軀體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:34.43,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}つくられたカラダを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:40.37,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}只望你能讚美一句可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:40.37,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}かわいいと ほめてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:45.01,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}月光朦朧 夜空群青
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:45.01,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}月がにじむ 夜空は群青
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.13,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}是相信這完美世界的藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.13,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}完璧な世界 信じてる Blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:54.91,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}流星啊 請帶我去往明日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:54.91,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}流星よ 明日へ つれていって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:59.71,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}機械結構是無法解讀的純情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:59.71,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}メカニズムは 読めない 純情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:03.52,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}與你萌生的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:03.52,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}君と芽生えた 友情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:07.16,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}眼中的淚水 流露出倔強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:07.16,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}涙 瞳は 強情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.86,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}向著自己堅信的方向轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.86,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}確信のほうへ シフト決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.91,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}方向不會動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.91,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}ベクトルはブレない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.92,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}We are flying kids
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.92,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}We are flying kids
