Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫降？你降去哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華平安著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 我這邊繼續執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮拜堂 操場 還有體育館的地下有構造物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當有規模啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是設施 到底是用來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了 就是巨型機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七神合體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～好強大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在電視購物上買到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認真說這種話！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是巨型宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 對了 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外星人在誘拐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是美少女失蹤事件的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了調查這個星球的生態系統 美少女們才會被抓的
